，偷情，同人妻人夫做愛，亂倫， 強姦，迷姦，撿屍<br />\n一有時間就諗下可以點樣屌到自己個呀嫂，堂/表姐妹，女朋友/老婆嘅姊妹，或者朋友個女，朋友個孫，弱智信徒嘅弱智女、 弱智孫女，老闆屌女秘書，醫生屌女病人，偷嘢女客人主動叫處男店員屌佢同幫佢口交<br />\n老師就想同自己個學生做下愛咁，學生又諗下點屌個大波miss<br />\n再唔係就係最鍾意做愛果時拍下片，方便以後分手再要脅下個前度做多幾次分手愛<br />\n台妹最馨同條仔吵兩句嘴就馬上搵前度傾心事，傾傾下就又做愛<br />\n個前度問佢可唔可以內射，台妹搖頭說不，但最後還是被射滿滿<br />\n所以話，呢個地方真係十分淫亂"},{"pid":"f130490599bef8c404e3c802c5ca6e24f0bd20c7","tid":568670,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:27:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/2-16-2018/TvAkIB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F2-16-2018%2FTvAkIB.gif&h=b12df9b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入球球員🇭🇰陳肇麒(香港飛馬)<br />\n<em>2018-02-24 17:30 東方vs 香港飛馬 港超 旺角大球場\t$80, $30</em>"},{"pid":"a658054cff479ffb6b42be4de37a1cdea18fe7e6","tid":568670,"uid":45842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f130490599bef8c404e3c802c5ca6e24f0bd20c7","tid":568670,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:27:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/2-16-2018/TvAkIB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F2-16-2018%2FTvAkIB.gif&h=b12df9b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入球球員🇭🇰陳肇麒(香港飛馬)<br />\n<em>2018-02-24 17:30 東方vs 香港飛馬 港超 旺角大球場\t$80, $30</em>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:34:20.000Z","msg":"大埔黎嫁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ffff595556b6aaf85269fc78be110cbedd8b160","tid":568670,"uid":168506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:35:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"830fdc7a0d11c43620739ec6ebb941e8c362d5e9","tid":568670,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:38:01.000Z","msg":"女方怕對方在內射，不敢掙扎？？？？<br />\n<br />\n正常怕佢射先掙扎，唔掙扎是想射到最入"},{"pid":"45d7b403822c81943272cdea040df00b6bba7e2b","tid":568670,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:39:20.000Z","msg":"不要暗戀，去強姦。人生沒有那麼多時間給你演內心戲。愛她就去搞她，喜歡就去強姦。表白有什麼用還是會被拒絕。追不到就下藥，翻臉就發裸照。大不了蹲監獄，你連監獄都不敢蹲還好意思說愛她。出來之後找到她繼續強姦，強姦到讓她開始懷疑自己的人生，讓她覺得她人生的意義就是被你強姦。"},{"pid":"4f9b00bc8f5625c8c7d073f0e852d5bedf5469b3","tid":568670,"uid":8636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:40:15.000Z","msg":"，並傳道歉貼圖<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母台狗真係好弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3b1c68af6e7eaabdc306023981a81a28d470f7c","tid":568670,"uid":88309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:42:15.000Z","msg":"萬華區加一分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e5277c3deba73d63677432e3395d83f655f5932","tid":568670,"uid":27049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:43:09.000Z","msg":"叫唔郁就唔郁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁聽話"},{"pid":"6b3455ab580f2db07491ce895e16cf219fbddefe","tid":568670,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e5277c3deba73d63677432e3395d83f655f5932","tid":568670,"uid":27049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:43:09.000Z","msg":"叫唔郁就唔郁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁聽話"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:46:50.000Z","msg":"台母豬好難唔聽話"},{"pid":"7291895f86f59aadfe6a67fcf77e4e0cc13fc9eb","tid":568670,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:48:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"630c9c657af1276008ec0553e816d4dfd187871d","tid":568670,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:55:04.000Z","msg":"黑男？"},{"pid":"364af17a699553f177674acde3f29be83ba22445","tid":568670,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:08:30.000Z","msg":"台灣人唔係淫<br />\n係戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca7ec15277a07b19b85dda56d16cad80046bd0e4","tid":568670,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a658054cff479ffb6b42be4de37a1cdea18fe7e6","tid":568670,"uid":45842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f130490599bef8c404e3c802c5ca6e24f0bd20c7","tid":568670,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:27:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/2-16-2018/TvAkIB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F2-16-2018%2FTvAkIB.gif&h=b12df9b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入球球員🇭🇰陳肇麒(香港飛馬)<br />\n<em>2018-02-24 17:30 東方vs 香港飛馬 港超 旺角大球場\t$80, $30</em>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:34:20.000Z","msg":"大埔黎嫁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:22:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">和富大埔憑盧卡斯及阿倫烈馬的入球，以2:1反勝香港飛馬，捧走今季菁英盃。<br />\n上半場2分鐘，盧卡斯右路窄位扣過守將後起腳，被基斯贊用腳擋出。8分鐘，盧卡斯禁區左路入楔快射被查維斯飛身剷出。15分鐘，伊達開出中路罰球但杜度窄位抽射不中目標。27分鐘，中村祐人扣入禁區頂起腳被基斯贊撲出。盧卡斯左路窄位快射再被基斯贊飛身擋出。35分鐘，陳俊樂右路傳中，盧卡斯近門車身窩利中楣不入。<span style=\"color: red;\">45分鐘，梁星耀解圍變回傳，保羅打手槌漏空被陳肇麒「執雞」頂入，飛馬半場領先1:0。</span></span>"}]}